file.name: flat-object-with-number-options.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: 'A sample object containing standard properties'
  title: 'Sample: flat object with number pattern'
  version: 1.3.3

components:
  schemas:

    FlatObjectWithNumberOptions:
      type: object
      description: Specifies a geographic location in terms of its Latitude and Longitude
      required:
        - latitude
      properties:
        latitude:
          type: number
          format: double
          description: 'The latitude in degrees. It must be in the range [-90.0, +90.0]'
          minimum: -90
          maximum: 90
        description:
          type: string
          minLength: 1
          maxLength: 10
